1
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:38,200
What he said at the table,

2
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:41,200
was what he wanted to tell you.

3
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:44,000
And it was also what I wanted to tell you.

4
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:46,759
Fate always plays tricks on us.

5
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:49,960
It separated us.

6
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:51,840
But today

7
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,520
it brought us together again.

8
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:54,920
But...

9
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:57,400
We're alive, aren't we?

10
00:01:58,720 --> 00:01:59,400
Isn't this

11
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,800
the happiest thing?

12
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:05,960
Yes.

13
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,920
The happiest thing.

14
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:10,180
Fate has no right or wrong.

15
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,760
Just accept it.

16
00:02:12,600 --> 00:02:13,560
Cherish it.

17
00:02:13,720 --> 00:02:14,640
That's enough,

18
00:02:15,040 --> 00:02:15,800
isn't it?

19
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:18,680
Accept it.

20
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:20,720
Cherish it.

21
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:37,840
Xiaoyue.

22
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:42,960
Wanfu.

23
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,090
Were you waiting for me?

24
00:02:49,600 --> 00:02:51,520
I came with Yunkui.

25
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:54,120
Let's let the two of them talk first.

26
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,600
That day,

27
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,480
I saw you were still alive.

28
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,160
I was so happy.

29
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,000
That day,

30
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:15,000
I saw you were alive too.

31
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,520
I was so happy too.

32
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,440
It's a small world.

33
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:26,000
Zhang Yunkui

34
00:03:27,760 --> 00:03:29,220
was my brigade commander.

35
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:30,560
How did you two

36
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,360
end up together?

37
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,800
I went to Wuhan with Miss Yu.

38
00:03:39,160 --> 00:03:40,200
I found out

39
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:41,520
Dachang had fallen.

40
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:44,450
And everyone in the 87th Brigade was gone.

41
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:46,000
I cried for days.

42
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,360
Later,

43
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:51,210
Yunkui went to Wuhan
to find Young Master Luo.

44
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:53,440
We met in the ruins of the Yu Family home.

45
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,600
After that,

46
00:03:56,079 --> 00:03:56,440
he led the evacuation

47
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:58,720
from the Wuhan Military Field Hospital.

48
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:01,160
And I went with them.

49
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:04,360
And gradually,

50
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:06,640
we ended up together.

51
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:09,520
Wanfu.

52
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:11,640
I heard you were gone.

53
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,680
I felt terrible.

54
00:04:12,880 --> 00:04:14,440
I even copied others.

55
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:16,040
I made you a tomb

56
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,440
by the Yangtze River.

57
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,040
You made me a tomb?

58
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:20,200
An empty tomb.

59
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,000
Well, of course it had to be

60
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,440
an empty tomb.

61
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:23,120
So...

62
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:23,860
Did you burn

63
00:04:23,880 --> 00:04:24,960
incense for me?

64
00:04:25,080 --> 00:04:26,280
Every holiday.

65
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:27,500
I never missed one.

66
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,880
No wonder all these years in Shanghai,

67
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,280
everything went so wrong for me.

68
00:04:31,280 --> 00:04:31,600
So on every holiday,

69
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,000
from thousands of li away,
someone was still thinking

70
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,920
of me.

71
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:39,880
Thank you.

72
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,960
So what about the gold hairpin I gave you?

73
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,420
Don't tell me you buried it

74
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:49,760
in that tomb too.

75
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,940
The New Fourth Army has a rule.

76
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:54,490
All female comrades must have short hair.

77
00:04:54,880 --> 00:04:56,740
It would've been useless anyway.

78
00:04:56,880 --> 00:04:58,320
When I was in Central Jiangsu

79
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,720
helping villagers flee,

80
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,320
I saw

81
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,120
fire-burners

82
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:03,440
burn down Uncle Li's house.

83
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,640
So I donated the hairpin.

84
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:06,840
For them to rebuild.

85
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,280
You donated it?

86
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,060
But that's what I saved...

87
00:05:15,280 --> 00:05:16,410
Good. You did right.

88
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,320
This

89
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,160
is what you gave me

90
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,320
when we parted.

91
00:05:29,760 --> 00:05:31,360
I remember all your private savings

92
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,280
were

93
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:34,159
in here.

94
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:37,080
It was 35.80 in total.

95
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:43,960
Tell me, should I give you back the 35.80

96
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,320
or add a bit more?

97
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:48,480
Wanfu.

98
00:05:49,280 --> 00:05:51,080
This is just an object.

99
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,880
You keep it.

100
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,040
Alright.

101
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,200
I'm used to it anyway.

102
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:01,000
So I'll keep it.

103
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,800
That day,

104
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:10,880
I suddenly saw you

105
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,880
with Zhang Yunkui.

106
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:15,560
I felt really awful.

107
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:18,680
It hurt so much.

108
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:21,000
But when I sobered up,

109
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,850
I realized I was being too selfish.

110
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:24,920
You said I'd become

111
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:26,600
a grave to you.

112
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,960
What more could I ask of you?

113
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:31,000
Ask you to remain faithful to me?

114
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,200
That's nonsense.

115
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:34,700
You did nothing wrong.

116
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:35,840
Besides,

117
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:38,159
Zhang Yunkui and I

118
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,800
crawled out of a pile of corpses together.

119
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,120
I've seen his bravery.

120
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:45,250
I've also seen his righteousness.

121
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,920
He's a reliable man.

122
00:06:47,880 --> 00:06:48,840
You chose right.

123
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,440
He's just a bad singer.

124
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,760
Wanfu,

125
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,720
you've changed so much.

126
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:59,680
You're completely different
from 6 years ago.

127
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,520
Yujiao is really wonderful too.

128
00:07:01,960 --> 00:07:03,620
I sincerely wish you the best.

129
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,560
You should trust Yujiao.

130
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:07,400
She witnessed your growth.

131
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,680
You should trust yourself.

132
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:17,290
Let's go inside.

133
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:36,210
Brigade Commander,

134
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,090
Regimental Commander,

135
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,159
Zhang Dougui,

136
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,960
Zhang Yunkui,

137
00:07:41,440 --> 00:07:42,480
which one should

138
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:43,480
I call you?

139
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,240
Kong Erbao,

140
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,240
Meng Wanfu,

141
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,720
He Bishi,

142
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,440
how should I address you?

143
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:55,040
Meng Wanfu.

144
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,760
Zhang Yunkui.

145
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:00,840
He was also Zhang Yunkui for a while.

146
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:01,560
I know.

147
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,480
Ding Yujiao.

148
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:13,320
Han Xiaoyue.

149
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,880
Enough personal talk.

150
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:17,810
Let's talk about

151
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,450
official business.

152
00:08:24,200 --> 00:08:25,460
Gun Inspection Order.

153
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:27,520
I think Ge Zhiyuan and Ge Zhanren

154
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,640
don't trust us.

155
00:08:28,880 --> 00:08:30,440
They want to use the Gun Inspection Order

156
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:31,120
to see if we've

157
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:32,360
truly defected.

158
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:34,559
Ge Zhiyuan and Ge Zhanren

159
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:35,559
must have

160
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:37,159
suspected you for a long time.

161
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:38,480
Last time at the table,

162
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,929
when you weren't there,

163
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:40,919
Ge Zhiyuan

164
00:08:41,120 --> 00:08:42,760
kept insinuating to me

165
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:44,420
that you're double-dealing.

166
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:45,690
And he also suspects

167
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:47,840
you have ties with the New Fourth Army.

168
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,680
Ge Zhanren

169
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,080
has already arrived in Nantong.

170
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,740
He went to find Zhao Nansheng.

171
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,060
That Zhao Nansheng

172
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,600
is ruthless.

173
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:56,140
This Gun Inspection Order

174
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:57,620
is just the first step.

175
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,360
They must have other methods

176
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,640
after this.

177
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:02,280
Actually, all they want

178
00:09:02,280 --> 00:09:03,480
is to divide us.

179
00:09:04,680 --> 00:09:05,680
If they divide us,

180
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:07,320
we can also divide them.

181
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:09,680
The Japanese lead the Rural Pacification.

182
00:09:09,680 --> 00:09:10,240
But

183
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,360
with not enough troops,

184
00:09:11,360 --> 00:09:13,220
they must rely on the puppet army.

185
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,400
But they don't trust them.

186
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,400
So what do they do?

187
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,200
They can only

188
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,760
limit and restrict them.

189
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,560
The Japanese for "Rural Pacification"
came from nowhere,

190
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:22,880
seizing all power.

191
00:09:23,280 --> 00:09:25,080
The local puppet army
is definitely not happy

192
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,360
about it.

193
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:27,520
So between them,

194
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,920
it'll only be dog-eat-dog.

195
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:29,680
Also,

196
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,000
the new and old

197
00:09:31,000 --> 00:09:31,880
puppet armies

198
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,650
have deep contradictions.

199
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:35,040
So we must exploit

200
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,840
these contradictions

201
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,640
and analyze them well.

202
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,500
We bring those we can't attack

203
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:41,720
to our side.

204
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:44,280
I understand.

205
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,840
We need to win over Ge Zhansong.

206
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:50,250
And then eliminate Ge Zhanren.

207
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:51,680
Exactly.

208
00:09:53,400 --> 00:09:55,640
Mom, I finished memorizing it.

209
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,760
So fast?

210
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:59,560
Then recite it for me.

211
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:02,480
I want to stay
in this spiritual place for a while,

212
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:05,160
but the sun is setting.

213
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:08,120
I bade the sun-god to stay his course,

214
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:11,040
gazing at Yanzi Mountain,
wishing time would not press on.

215
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:13,840
The road ahead is long and arduous.

216
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:16,840
I shall seek high and low in my quest.

217
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:18,680
Very good.

218
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:25,080
Yueming,

219
00:10:25,520 --> 00:10:26,400
come here.

220
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,640
You recited that poem

221
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:31,200
so well.

222
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,240
I have a gift for you.

223
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,000
Keep working this hard and memorize

224
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,840
every poem this well,

225
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:01,720
okay?

226
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:03,840
Alright,

227
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:04,760
it's getting late.

228
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:05,720
Rest early.

229
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,170
We're heading back.

230
00:11:13,880 --> 00:11:15,120
Thank you, Uncle.

231
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,120
Yueming.

232
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,280
That was the first time

233
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:52,640
you saw your biological father.

234
00:11:53,040 --> 00:11:55,320
And the only time.

235
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:58,000
He gave you a broad bean.

236
00:11:58,200 --> 00:11:58,640
Now,

237
00:11:58,640 --> 00:12:00,920
do you know how much that broad bean

238
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:03,560
means to Mom?

239
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:05,600
I wished so much

240
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:08,120
that you could call him Dad.

241
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:10,080
But you

242
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,360
couldn't.

243
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:15,920
I hope

244
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:16,960
you always remember

245
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:20,320
your father's figure
when he left for the last time.

246
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:23,320
With Wanfu's dad's help,

247
00:12:23,520 --> 00:12:27,200
Yunkui's father successfully completed
his undercover mission.

248
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:29,120
After the Gun Inspection Order passed,

249
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:31,200
he received a new mission.

250
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:38,240
To win the fight
against "Rural Pacification,"

251
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,520
and to secure and expand

252
00:12:39,520 --> 00:12:40,920
the anti-Japanese base.

253
00:12:41,040 --> 00:12:42,160
The military decided

254
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:43,400
to fight a major battle.

255
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:44,320
To seize the transport hub
of Central Jiangsu

256
00:12:44,320 --> 00:12:45,760
and Northern Jiangsu,

257
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,760
Wenqiao Town.

258
00:12:48,840 --> 00:12:49,640
Wenqiao Town is a heavily fortified

259
00:12:49,640 --> 00:12:51,240
military stronghold.

260
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:52,730
Around the garrison

261
00:12:52,920 --> 00:12:54,920
are over 10 bunkers, visible and hidden,

262
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:55,640
forming

263
00:12:55,920 --> 00:12:57,720
a plum blossom-shaped defense.

264
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,400
So the military region decided

265
00:12:59,400 --> 00:13:01,000
to mobilize
the Central Jiangsu Military Region

266
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,480
and 4 other sub-districts,

267
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:03,920
a total of 5 regiments,

268
00:13:04,000 --> 00:13:06,640
to fight a head-to-head
heart-stabbing battle.

269
00:13:06,640 --> 00:13:07,800
But Wenqiao Town is located

270
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:09,080
in a central area.

271
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:11,080
Reinforcements have many routes.

272
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:12,400
We must attack strongholds

273
00:13:12,400 --> 00:13:14,260
and block their reinforcements.

274
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:15,410
What is our mission?

275
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,400
Your mission has 3 steps.

276
00:13:17,920 --> 00:13:18,520
First,

277
00:13:18,680 --> 00:13:19,840
before the uprising,

278
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,880
organize sailors

279
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:21,840
and dock workers

280
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:23,440
to get supplies

281
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:25,600
to the main forces in Central Jiangsu.

282
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:26,330
Second step.

283
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,840
Mobilize the militia,

284
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:28,680
cut the roads,

285
00:13:28,840 --> 00:13:29,640
bury mines,

286
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:31,400
and block enemy reinforcements.

287
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:32,060
Third step:

288
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:33,580
The regiment revolts.

289
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,440
Attack Japanese

290
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:35,600
and Zhao Nansheng reinforcements

291
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,000
heading to Wenqiao Town.

292
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:37,920
Meanwhile,

293
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:39,880
all of Central Jiangsu will coordinate

294
00:13:39,880 --> 00:13:40,840
to mobilize the masses

295
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:41,970
and burn the fences.

